<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1)Zo gun Yesu, zo gun Yesu
 Zo gun Yesu yanzu.
 Yanzu, zo gun Yesu.
 Zo gun Yesu yanzu.

[V2]
 2)Karɓi ceto, karɓi ceto,
 Karɓi ceto yanzu.
 Yanzu, karɓi ceto
 Karɓi ceto yanzu.

[V3]
 3)To, na yarda, i, na yarda
 Ni na yarda yanzu.
 Yanzu dai na yarda,
 Zan bi Yesu yanzu.</lyrics>
<title>Zo Gun Yesu, Zo Gun Yesu Y46</title>
<hymn_number>46</hymn_number>
</song>